Eldest Young Master, apologies for not greeting you sooner.

5
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:05,700
What were you doing? Why didn't you announce Eldest Young Master's arrival?

6
00:02:05,700 --> 00:02:07,950
My apologies, sir.

7
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:10,950
You seemed busy, so I told him to stay quiet.

8
00:02:10,950 --> 00:02:12,500
You're...?

