00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:17,540
It's nothing important. Just a sketch to keep my hands practicing.

11
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:22,020
Here. Take these to the study.

12
00:02:26,710 --> 00:02:28,460
Eldest Young Master?

13
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:34,230
I came by today to see if you'd join me for some drinks and music.

14
00:02:34,230 --> 00:02:38,010
You've been working nonstop. You need some relaxation.

15
00:02:38,010 --> 00:02:42,150
You may not know this, but my alcohol tolerance is very low.

16
00:02:42,150 --> 00:02:45,460
Even a sip gets me drunk, and once I'm drunk,

17
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:50,000
I ramble and say all the things I shouldn't say.

18
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:53,680
Let's just enjoy the music. Skip the drinks.

19
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:55,870
Fair enough. Just the music.

20
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:58,000
I promise you won't get even a sip of alcohol.

21
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:00,560
Come on. Let's go.

22
00:03:03,020 --> 00:03:05,800
   

23
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,370
Where was I?

24
00:03:07,370 --> 00:03:10,870
- You've already said too much. 
 - No, don't interrupt.

25
00:03:10,870 --> 00:03:13,330
I remember now. Yes...

26
00:03:13,330 --> 00:03:17,900
That Chu Huaiming! That bastard... He made my life miserable...

27
00:03:17,900 --> 00:03:20,750
Zang Hai, my friend, your alcohol tolerance really is...

28
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:22,750
Official Zang... Official Zang...

29
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:27,090
- Why did you drink so much? 
 - Come on. Help your master inside to rest.

30
00:03:27,090 --> 00:03:30,360
Official Zhuang, it's so late. Shall I send someone to escort you home?

31
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:34,140
No need. I'm exhausted, too.

32
00:03:34,140 --> 00:03:39,550
I'll just stay here tonight. Find me a room later.

33
00:03:39,550 --> 00:03:41,200
Yes, sir.

34
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,460
- Official Zang, come on. 
 - Where are we going?

35
00:03:42,460 --> 00:03:45,780
Back to your room. Easy now.

36
00:03:45,780 --> 00:03:49,000
- Where are we going? 
 - To your room, sir.

37
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:51,110
Take it slow.

38
00:04:35,580 --> 00:04:40,034
   

39
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:53,660
Official Zhuang has worked hard. Take him to rest.

40
00:04:53,660 --> 00:04:55,340
Yes, sir.

41
00:05:09,620 --> 00:05:13,870
Father, this looks like the structure of some kind of box,

42
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:16,510
along with instructions for disabling its mechanism.

43
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:20,660
And the thing to the side is a bronze fish.

44
00:05:22,730 --> 00:05:28,810
Indeed. Zhuang Luyin even told Zang Hai about the bronze fish.

45
00:05:28,810 --> 00:05:33,270
It really is connected to the Gui Seal.

46
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,650
This...

47
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:43,950
Could it be that Zhuang Luyin already has the seal?

48
00:05:43,950 --> 00:05:46,390
What will you do, Father?

49
00:05:46,390 --> 00:05:51,560
This time, I'm going to confirm it myself.

50
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:59,000
Xiao Hai, Zhuang Zhifu sent word.

51
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:02,400
He's inviting you to lunch tomorrow at Zuichun Pavilion.

52
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:24,000
Brother Zang Hai,

53
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:28,800
this here is Zuichun Pavilion's newest fine wine.

54
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:32,410
It's smooth and rich. You've got to give it a proper try.

55
00:06:32,410 --> 00:06:34,870
Today is a joyous day.

56
00:06:34,870 --> 00:06:37,120
We can't go home until we're drunk.

57
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,730
Here.

58
00:06:38,730 --> 00:06:42,900
Thank you, Eldest Young Master. I'll listen to you.

59
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:44,610
Cheers.

60
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:52,470
- What do you think? 
 - It's excellent.

61
00:06:52,470 --> 00:06:57,350
Since you like it, have a few more cups. Come on.

62
00:07:00,340 --> 00:07:01,930
Please.

63
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,650
Great! One more.

64
00:07:08,650 --> 00:07:13,590
Eldest Young Master, maybe we should have some food first.

65
00:07:14,430 --> 00:07:19,150
Brother Zang Hai, if you want to stay in everyone's good graces at court,

66
00:07:19,150 --> 00:07:23,240
you'll need to learn to hold your liquor.

67
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:27,510
So, today, let me help you train.

68
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:20,100
Zang Hai.

69
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:24,480
You're drunk.

70
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:27,050
No, you're drunk.

71
00:08:34,140 --> 00:08:39,920
Did you find that thing my father asked you to find?

72
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:42,120
What thing?

73
00:08:47,550 --> 00:08:52,870
I thought that after the past few days, we were already friends.

74
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:54,850
Friends?

75
00:08:55,650 --> 00:09:00,020
Wasn't it your mother who went to the Marquis to speak ill of me?

76
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:02,150
Didn't you two try to get me kicked out?

77
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:04,640
Don't think I don't know.

78
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:12,630
You really dare say that to my face?

79
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:15,430
Why wouldn't I? Why wouldn't I?

80
00:09:15,430 --> 00:09:19,550
Let me tell you! Do you have any idea how much the Marquis values me now?

81
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:23,440
I'm more capable than any of you ever imagined.

82
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:25,120
Come on.

83
00:09:32,370 --> 00:09:36,410
Brother, I admit it.

84
00:09:36,410 --> 00:09:40,920
Being close with Yang Zhen and the others made me somewhat biased against you.

85
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:45,190
But we have to look ahead, right?

86
00:09:46,030 --> 00:09:52,180
Honestly, I'm just like my father â€“ I admire you so much.

87
00:09:52,180 --> 00:09:54,750
From now on, we'll only grow closer.

88
00:09:54,750 --> 00:10:00,550
I really hope you'll treat me as a friend you can speak freely to.

89
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:06,970
A friend I can say anything to...

90
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:09,910
I'm so glad you see me...

91
00:10:11,100 --> 00:10:12,940
as a friend.

92
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:26,620
So, Brother Zang, tell me.

93
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:30,430
Did you find that thing my father asked you to find?

94
00:10:33,410 --> 00:10:36,910
The Gui Seal? You mean the Gui Seal?

95
00:10:39,630 --> 00:10:43,200
The Marquis indeed mentioned it.

96
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:48,490
He said he went through so much just to track it down.

97
00:10:48,490 --> 00:10:52,490
He said that with the Gui Seal,

98
00:10:52,490 --> 00:10:55,980
anything's possible.

99
00:10:57,970 --> 00:11:00,200
Anything's possible...

100
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:03,450
Hey, don't pass out!

101
00:11:03,450 --> 00:11:06,120
So, did you find it or not? Where is it?

102
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:09,780
Did I find it? No...

103
00:11:09,780 --> 00:11:12,900
Zang Hai. Don't go, Zang Hai. Come back here.

104
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:15,630
Careful.

105
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:18,206
What's wrong?

106
00:11:18,206 --> 00:11:22,080
I can't. I can't say...

107
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:27,120
The Marquis told me never to tell outsiders.

108
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:30,640
Outsiders? Am I an outsider?

109
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:35,900
I swear I won't tell a soul. All right?

110
00:11:37,180 --> 00:11:38,830
Hey.

111
00:11:45,140 --> 00:11:48,900
I bet Father never told you anything.

112
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:51,420
You think he values it? No way!

113
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,040
Nonsense!

114
00:11:56,730 --> 00:11:58,250
Come here.

115
00:11:58,870 --> 00:12:00,470
Come closer!

116
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:12,890
The thing is in the underground vault of the Marquis's treasury.

117
00:12:18,750 --> 00:12:20,350
Zang Hai?

118
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:24,480
Zang Hai?

119
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:27,660
Zang Hai?

120
00:12:30,670 --> 00:12:32,350
Sir.

121
00:12:33,970 --> 00:12:35,580
Sir.

122
00:12:38,300 --> 00:12:39,630
Did you hear all that?

123
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:42,810
I got him to talk.

124
00:13:00,270 --> 00:13:05,910
He said the Marquis found the Gui Seal

125
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:10,450
and hid it in the treasury of the Marquis' residence.

126
00:13:10,450 --> 00:13:13,830
You didn't know?

127
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:17,710
So, the Marquis never told you?

128
00:13:17,710 --> 00:13:21,550
I've never heard my father mention that.

129
00:13:23,550 --> 00:13:25,330
Zhifu,

130
00:13:25,910 --> 00:13:28,270
there's something you need to know.

131
00:13:28,270 --> 00:13:34,900
What he just said is your father's biggest secret.

132
00:13:34,900 --> 00:13:39,390
Your father told him all of these secrets.

133
00:13:39,390 --> 00:13:46,120
That makes him your father's true confidant.

134
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:49,630
But now, he's chosen to side with your younger brother.

135
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:51,000
What does that tell you?

136
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:56,590
As long as he's around, Zhuang Zhixing will be the heir of the Zhuang household.

137
00:13:57,550 --> 00:13:59,500
Impossible!

138
00:13:59,500 --> 00:14:03,480
I'm the rightful heir. I'm the son of my father's principal wife!

139
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:08,290
Your mother, Jiang Xiang, may remain in favor,

140
00:14:08,290 --> 00:14:12,380
but it's not what it once was.

141
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:18,360
How much can she do for you now?

142
00:14:20,930 --> 00:14:22,830
Jiang Xiang...

143
00:14:23,810 --> 00:14:26,850
Jiang Xiang killed Shen.

144
00:14:28,550 --> 00:14:31,200
What are you talking about?

145
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:35,480
I'm not making it up. Everyone knows.

146
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,320
Even Zhuang Zhixing knows.

147
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:42,440
No... No.

148
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:45,020
Zhifu, how about this?

149
00:14:45,020 --> 00:14:51,250
Zang Hai may have sided with your brother, but I can side with you.

150
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:06,750
Kill him, and I'll guarantee your wealth and power.

151
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:08,420
What do you say?

152
00:15:10,550 --> 00:15:15,640
As long as you kill him, Zhuang Zhixing will go back to his old self.

153
00:15:15,640 --> 00:15:18,630
On his own, he's no threat.

154
00:15:18,630 --> 00:15:23,360
And the position as the Zhuang family's head will surely be yours.

155
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,300
What are you waiting for?

156
00:15:41,300 --> 00:15:43,720
I... I'm sorry!

157
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:47,810
Eldest Young Master...

158
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,560
Eldest Young Master...

159
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:55,050
Why... Why...

160
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:14,250
Good boy. From now on, I'll do everything in my power to help you.

161
00:16:55,030 --> 00:16:56,730
Hang in there.

162
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:59,210
Father!

163
00:18:03,440 --> 00:18:05,180
Father.

164
00:18:05,910 --> 00:18:09,580
Someone rescued Zang Hai.

165
00:18:09,580 --> 00:18:11,310
Did you see who?

166
00:18:11,310 --> 00:18:13,530
His guard.

167
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:19,200
So, Zang Hai didn't die.

168
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:24,250
That complicates things.

169
00:18:26,410 --> 00:18:28,830
Sir, what do you mean?

170
00:18:28,830 --> 00:18:32,550
Official Zhuang, you're not only corrupt,

171
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:37,260
but you also tried to kill a court official.

172
00:18:37,260 --> 00:18:39,530
- No, I didn't. 
 - Guards.

173
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:41,690
What are you doing?

174
00:18:41,690 --> 00:18:44,030
Since you won't admit it,

175
00:18:44,030 --> 00:18:49,340
just wait for the Imperial Surveillance Office to get to the bottom of things.

176
00:18:49,340 --> 00:18:50,540
Come with us.

177
00:18:50,540 --> 00:18:53,480
Sir... I already did everything you told me to do!

178
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:55,180
Shut up!

179
00:19:01,270 --> 00:19:02,750
Shi Lei, drive us, now!

180
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:04,350
Got it.

181
00:19:08,210 --> 00:19:10,640
Master is tailing Cao Jingxian as planned.

182
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:13,110
We should head back and stop the bleeding.

183
00:19:13,110 --> 00:19:15,340
We can't go back. I can still hold on.

184
00:19:15,340 --> 00:19:19,560
You won't last much longer. You'll bleed to death!

185
00:19:19,560 --> 00:19:22,750
We can't change the plan. Take me to the Marquis Residence.

186
00:19:22,750 --> 00:19:24,720
Xiao Hai, are you insane? You'll die!

187
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:28,680
Trust me. I know what I'm doing.

188
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:31,040
Take me to the Marquis Residence!

189
00:19:34,610 --> 00:19:36,440
Shi Lei, to the Marquis Residence.

190
00:19:36,440 --> 00:19:38,010
Got it.

191
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:48,740
My Lord! My Lord! My Lord!

192
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:51,750
- What's wrong? Why the panic? 
 - Something happened!

193
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:52,930
Why are you bleeding?

194
00:19:52,930 --> 00:19:55,000
This isn't my blood.

195
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:58,460
It's Official Zang's. He's badly hurt.

196
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:02,590
Zang Hai!

197
00:20:05,780 --> 00:20:07,580
Stop standing around. Get a physician!

198
00:20:07,580 --> 00:20:09,240
Yes, My Lord.

199
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:10,780
What happened?

200
00:20:10,780 --> 00:20:16,190
My Lord... I can't hold on much longer,

201
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:21,450
but there's something I must tell you.

202
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:26,200
The one who tried to kill me today... was...

203
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,210
Who was it?

204
00:20:27,210 --> 00:20:29,060
It was...

205
00:20:30,030 --> 00:20:32,430
Eldest Young Master.

206
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:38,650
Zhifu tried to kill you?

207
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:42,580
He invited me to lunch.

208
00:20:42,580 --> 00:20:46,640
Then he suddenly attacked me.

209
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:51,580
Then... Cao Jingxian showed up.

210
00:20:51,580 --> 00:20:53,820
Cao Jingxian?

211
00:20:58,850 --> 00:21:03,720
Cao Jingxian must have some leverage over Eldest Young Master

212
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:06,520
so he was forced to attack me.

213
00:21:10,060 --> 00:21:12,880
Eldest Young Master must be in danger now.

214
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:16,350
Hurry... Go save him!

215
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:19,320
Zang Hai. Zang Hai!

216
00:21:20,030 --> 00:21:21,820
You can't die now.

217
00:21:21,820 --> 00:21:23,860
Hang in there!

218
00:21:23,860 --> 00:21:28,060
Zang Hai? Zang Hai! Where's the physician?

219
00:22:14,110 --> 00:22:16,030
My Lord.

220
00:22:16,030 --> 00:22:17,570
Come in.

221
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:29,540
My Lord, the Imperial Surveillance Office still won't release him.

222
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:39,340
Zhuang Shan, go summon two people for me:

223
00:22:39,340 --> 00:22:42,700
Xu Daishan, the Deputy Censor-in-Chief of the Censorate,

224
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:45,080
and Qi Ming, the Assistant Censor.

225
00:22:45,080 --> 00:22:46,570
Understood.

226
00:22:52,820 --> 00:23:00,880
Xu Daishan and Qi Ming have been visiting the Marquis Residence frequently.

227
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:04,960
They and the Marquis of Pingjin are very close now.

228
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:09,090
Father, the Marquis's birthday is in a few days

229
00:23:09,090 --> 00:23:11,960
I've heard he's planning a grand banquet.

230
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:15,930
And this time, he's invited many officials who don't see eye to eye with you.

231
00:23:15,930 --> 00:23:20,790
Looks like the past doesn't matter to him anymore.

232
00:23:20,790 --> 00:23:25,360
Now that he has the Gui Seal, he's ready to move against me.

233
