234
00:23:43,900 --> 00:23:45,560
Master...

235
00:23:48,440 --> 00:23:50,190
Master.

236
00:23:53,730 --> 00:23:56,680
Boy, you're finally awake.

237
00:23:56,680 --> 00:23:59,630
Once your condition stabilized, the Marquis had you sent back.

238
00:23:59,630 --> 00:24:02,280
You've been out for days.

239
00:24:04,960 --> 00:24:06,460
Easy now.

240
00:24:12,830 --> 00:24:14,480
Here, Xiao Hai.

241
00:24:21,790 --> 00:24:23,490
Take it slow.

242
00:24:29,510 --> 00:24:32,960
Master, how are things at the Marquis Residence?

243
00:24:32,960 --> 00:24:35,610
Zhuang Zhifu got detained by the Imperial Surveillance Office that day

244
00:24:35,610 --> 00:24:37,100
and hasn't returned since.

245
00:24:37,100 --> 00:24:41,150
The Marquis of Pingjin has invited his allies from the Censorate to the residence.

246
00:24:41,150 --> 00:24:44,840
Looks like he's rallying support from officials to impeach Cao Jingxian.

247
00:24:44,840 --> 00:24:46,350
So, he believed me.

248
00:24:46,350 --> 00:24:50,880
Your act really caught him off guard.

249
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:52,590
Only by doing this

250
00:24:52,590 --> 00:24:55,960
will the Marquis of Pingjin believe me, no matter what I say.

251
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:59,960
I think Cao Jingxian already knows...

252
