while also finding the seal,

262
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:25,150
I'd need help from someone. And this person would need to know what happened back then.

263
00:26:26,010 --> 00:26:29,960
That person is very likely my third enemy.

264
00:26:33,010 --> 00:26:35,030
Shi Lei and I will keep watch on the Cao Residence.

265
00:26:35,030 --> 00:26:38,050
We'll alert you as soon as Cao Jingxian makes a move.

266
00:26:43,790 --> 00:26:45,590
You hungry?

267
00:26:45,590 --> 00:26:47,000
I've had food prepared for you for a while.

268
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:48,680
I'll go get it.

269
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:25,790
Xiao Hai.

270
00:27:25,790 --> 00:27:27,190
Xiao Hai!

271
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:30,650
Cao Jingxian finally left his residence.

272
00:27:30,650 --> 00:27:32,640
I've sent Shi Lei to tail him.

273
00:27:32,640 --> 00:27:34,510
The Marquis of Pingjin has forced his hand.

274
00:27:34,510 --> 00:27:36,210
I'm going after him.

275
00:27:36,210 --> 00:27:38,310
You're still recovering.

276
00:27:38,310 --> 00:27:39,750
No time to worry about that.

277
00:27:39,750 --> 00:27:44,210
Wait... At least put on more clothes!

278
00:28:34,100 --> 00:28:36,651
   

279
