280
00:28:58,400 --> 00:29:02,880
Sir, wh-what is this place?

281
00:29:02,880 --> 00:29:06,530
It's the residence that the officials have given to a hostage.

282
00:29:07,350 --> 00:29:11,750
So, your third enemy l-lives here, too?

283
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:13,510
I can't say for sure.

284
00:29:13,510 --> 00:29:14,970
I'll only know if I get inside.

285
00:29:14,970 --> 00:29:18,350
But there are so many Surveillance Officers outside.

286
00:29:18,350 --> 00:29:20,470
How are we supposed to get in?

287
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:53,690
Hey.

288
00:29:57,030 --> 00:30:00,160
What... What are you doing?

289
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:02,070
The land route is blocked,

290
00:30:02,070 --> 00:30:04,200
so I'll go in through the water.

291
00:30:04,200 --> 00:30:06,200
I know the city's layout.

292
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:09,310
There's an underground channel that leads to the residence.

293
00:30:09,310 --> 00:30:13,420
- But sir... 
 - Shi Lei, wait for me here.

294
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:05,980
 Your Highness, I came tonight to discuss something important. 

295
00:31:06,780 --> 00:31:09,960
 I know where the Gui Seal is already. 

296
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:13,750
 I'm willing to tell you everything, but... 

297
00:31:13,750 --> 00:31:17,880
 you must honor our agreement. 

298
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:21,440
 If you're here to see me before even getting the seal, 

299
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:25,030
 it must be hidden somewhere that's giving you trouble. 

300
00:31:25,030 --> 00:31:27,310
 You're sharp as ever, Your Highness. 

301
00:31:27,310 --> 00:31:32,550
 To be frank, I'm indeed not fully confident I can retrieve it. 

302
00:31:32,550 --> 00:31:37,400
 But I'm willing to be open with you. 

303
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:41,100
Let's talk and see how we can both come out ahead.

304
00:31:41,100 --> 00:31:42,680
Sure.

305
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:44,720
We'll stick to our deal.

306
00:31:44,720 --> 00:31:48,720
Then could you tell me

307
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:53,750
how to use this Gui Seal, Your Highness?

308
00:31:53,750 --> 00:31:57,260
You'll know when we get it.

309
00:31:57,790 --> 00:32:03,790
I'm certain the Gui Seal is in the Marquis's hands.

310
00:32:03,790 --> 00:32:07,880
It's hidden beneath his treasury.

311
00:32:07,880 --> 00:32:11,750
 Zhuang Luyin is hosting a banquet the night after tomorrow. 

312
00:32:11,750 --> 00:32:14,310
 I plan to show up uninvited. 

313
00:32:14,310 --> 00:32:18,030
If we work together,

314
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:22,180
getting the seal will be easy.

315
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:28,290
 Aren't you afraid I'll disappear with it once I have it? 

316
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:31,960
 Surely you jest, Your Highness. 

317
00:32:31,960 --> 00:32:33,830
 You're a royal hostage from Dongxia. 

318
00:32:33,830 --> 00:32:37,590
What will happen if you vanish?

319
00:32:37,590 --> 00:32:42,790
I think you know that better than I do.

320
00:32:42,790 --> 00:32:46,030
 Since it was I who came to you back then, 

321
00:32:46,030 --> 00:32:49,070
 of course I'd come prepared. 

322
00:32:49,070 --> 00:32:54,700
 As long as the seal is in our hands, everything is negotiable. 

323
00:32:55,350 --> 00:33:00,440
I've searched for it long enough.

324
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:02,490
I can't wait any longer.

325
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:07,480
I'm out.

326
00:33:41,070 --> 00:33:44,020
Sir! Are you all right?

327
00:33:55,300 --> 00:33:59,140
So, the third person is the hostage princess from Dongxia?

328
00:34:02,480 --> 00:34:05,440
They say she hasn't left her mansion over the past ten years.

329
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:08,000
No one's even seen her face.

330
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:14,440
She arrived in the capital the day before your family fell.

331
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:18,980
But she was only ten back then.

332
00:34:20,970 --> 00:34:23,770
History has no shortage of prodigies

333
00:34:23,770 --> 00:34:27,650
who outsmart adults from a young age.

334
00:34:28,230 --> 00:34:31,780
Besides, I heard their conversation clearly.

335
00:34:34,000 --> 00:34:35,820
It makes sense.

336
00:34:35,820 --> 00:34:37,970
The Gui Seal is Dongxia's greatest treasure.

337
00:34:37,970 --> 00:34:40,760
Your father took it from Dongxia.

338
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:42,590
She has no reason not to look for it.

339
00:34:42,590 --> 00:34:43,990
Here.

340
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:53,850
Since Cao Jingxian has decided to act, she won't stand by and watch.

341
00:34:53,850 --> 00:34:57,110
She won't let him take the Gui Seal alone.

342
00:34:57,110 --> 00:35:00,510
Therefore, she'll show up.

343
00:35:02,150 --> 00:35:04,590
I'll keep watch there,

344
00:35:04,590 --> 00:35:06,610
waiting for my enemies.

345
00:35:10,920 --> 00:35:12,780
Two!

346
00:35:12,780 --> 00:35:14,700
Three!

347
00:35:14,700 --> 00:35:16,630
Four!

348
00:35:16,630 --> 00:35:18,490
Five!

349
00:35:18,490 --> 00:35:20,440
Six!

350
00:35:20,440 --> 00:35:22,280
Seven!

351
00:35:22,280 --> 00:35:24,030
Eight!

352
00:35:24,030 --> 00:35:26,530
Sir, someone's here to see you.

353
00:35:34,710 --> 00:35:36,060
Keep going!

354
00:35:36,060 --> 00:35:38,050
One!

355
00:35:38,050 --> 00:35:40,380
Two!

356
00:35:40,380 --> 00:35:42,730
Three!

357
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:45,820
What brings you here to see me today?

358
00:35:46,820 --> 00:35:49,650
I have something very important to tell you.

359
00:35:53,550 --> 00:35:55,000
You're off duty tomorrow, right?

360
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:56,150
Yes.

361
00:35:56,150 --> 00:35:58,740
It's Father's birthday tomorrow. I've prepared a gift.

362
00:35:58,740 --> 00:36:00,240
What's wrong?

363
00:36:01,280 --> 00:36:04,650
Tomorrow night, the Marquis is hosting a banquet for many close allies

364
00:36:04,650 --> 00:36:07,780
to discuss impeaching Cao Jingxian.

365
00:36:07,780 --> 00:36:11,010
And Cao Jingxian has already caught wind of it.

366
00:36:11,010 --> 00:36:13,550
He'll definitely show up.

367
00:36:13,550 --> 00:36:15,110
What's going to happen?

368
00:36:15,110 --> 00:36:20,320
Knowing your father and Cao Jingxian, there will be a clash.

369
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:25,110
What do you want me to do?

370
00:36:25,110 --> 00:36:30,450
Tell me. How's your relationship with your men these days?

371
00:36:30,450 --> 00:36:33,940
If I want you to return to the Marquis residence to rescue your father tomorrow night,

372
00:36:33,940 --> 00:36:35,860
will they assist you?

373
00:36:36,820 --> 00:36:38,700
They follow my lead now.

374
00:36:38,700 --> 00:36:40,280
It shouldn't be a problem.

375
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,780
Good.

376
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:47,260
Then I want you to gather your men and charge back to the residence tomorrow night.

377
00:36:47,860 --> 00:36:53,410
Only in a moment of true crisis like this will your father see your worth.

378
00:36:54,660 --> 00:36:58,890
It'll mean thousands more than any birthday gift.

379
00:37:02,260 --> 00:37:05,880
I'm not asking you to do this out of filial duty.

380
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:07,810
But rather for your own sake.

381
00:37:09,610 --> 00:37:12,450
Zhuang Zhifu's situation is dire now.

382
00:37:12,450 --> 00:37:16,090
This is your best chance.

383
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:20,320
When do we move?

384
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:22,210
Wait for my signal.

385
00:37:27,580 --> 00:37:31,995
   

386
00:37:42,570 --> 00:37:44,180
Wait here.

387
00:37:44,180 --> 00:37:45,640
Yes, sir.

388
00:38:45,360 --> 00:38:48,450
Miss Xiang, your swordsmanship is truly impressive.

389
00:38:48,450 --> 00:38:50,360
What brings you here?

390
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:53,480
I just felt like taking a walk today.

391
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:56,550
And somehow, I ended up here at Zhen Tower.

392
00:38:56,550 --> 00:38:57,920
What a coincidence.

