Last time, I said you'd have to trade your secret for mine.

396
00:39:10,720 --> 00:39:13,110
But I've changed my mind.

397
00:39:13,110 --> 00:39:17,010
I can tell you everything without you needing to reveal anything to me.

398
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:23,590
You're not curious anymore?

