419
00:40:22,700 --> 00:40:26,360
The Marquis has helped you, but haven't I done a lot for you, too?

420
00:40:30,030 --> 00:40:32,280
If you're willing to share your secret,

421
00:40:32,280 --> 00:40:34,790
