422
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:38,150
How about this?

423
00:40:38,150 --> 00:40:40,440
Wait for me a little longer tomorrow night.

424
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:42,780
We can talk later.

425
00:40:42,780 --> 00:40:44,160
Don't even think about it.

426
00:40:44,160 --> 00:40:48,670
If you're not there by Xu hour, you'll never hear that secret.

427
00:40:57,550 --> 00:40:58,710
All right.

428
00:40:58,710 --> 00:41:00,360
You have my word.

429
00:41:01,550 --> 00:41:03,000
Then it's settled.

430
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:04,670
See you tomorrow night.

431
00:41:26,090 --> 00:41:28,740
Miss, are you really going to tell him?

432
00:41:28,740 --> 00:41:31,800
There's no point in hiding it anymore.

433
00:41:31,800 --> 00:41:33,510
You'll go in my place.

434
00:41:33,510 --> 00:41:35,410
There will be a brutal clash at the Marquis's banquet tomorrow.

435
00:41:35,410 --> 00:41:38,220
I want him far away from it and out of harm's way.

436
00:41:38,220 --> 00:41:39,510
Stay by his side.

437
00:41:39,510 --> 00:41:41,110
Whatever happens, don't let him leave.

438
00:41:41,110 --> 00:41:42,610
No, I need to protect you.

439
00:41:42,610 --> 00:41:45,520
Once it's over, I'll go and meet him.

440
00:41:51,060 --> 00:41:56,230
   

