442
00:42:00,380 --> 00:42:02,480
You're my most trusted men.

443
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:04,860
I've taken care of you for years.

444
00:42:04,860 --> 00:42:07,440
Now it's time for you to repay me.

445
00:42:07,440 --> 00:42:10,130
 - We pledge our lives to you, sir! 
