00:42:21,190 --> 00:42:24,530
Guan Feng, don't mess up your part.

452
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:29,150
Master, I'm heading out.

453
00:42:29,150 --> 00:42:30,670
Be careful.

454
00:42:30,670 --> 00:42:33,010
We'll stick to the plan.

455
00:42:35,340 --> 00:42:40,100
Guan Feng, when you see her, tell her I got drunk at the banquet.

